# athena credentials & environment — TEMPLATE
#
# Copy this to ~/.athena/.env  (Windows: C:\Users\<you>\.athena\.env) and fill
# in ONLY the keys you need. Ollama (the default) needs NONE of these — they're
# for hosted providers and optional features.
#
# Format: KEY=value per line; '#' comments and blank lines OK; surrounding
# quotes are stripped. Recommend mode 0600.
# Lookup order at runtime: ~/.athena/.env  ->  process environment.
#
# Hosted-provider keys are usually added with:
#     athena providers add-key <provider> --key sk-...
# but can also live here.

# ── Hosted model providers (optional; Ollama is the default) ──────────────
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=...

# ── Optional feature credentials ──────────────────────────────────────────
# xAI / Grok Imagine video generation (from console.x.ai):
# ATHENA_XAI_API_KEY=...
# XAI_API_KEY=...
# X (Twitter) v2 search API:
# ATHENA_X_BEARER_TOKEN=...
# Discord gateway adapter:
# ATHENA_DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=...
# Web search:
# BRAVE_API_KEY=...
# ATHENA_SEARCH_BACKEND=brave              # or: searxng
# ATHENA_SEARXNG_URL=http://localhost:8888
# Future video backends:
# ATHENA_RUNWAY_API_KEY=...
# ATHENA_PIKA_API_KEY=...

# ── Behavior toggles / overrides ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Force a specific JS runtime for the TUI (default: auto — node, then bun):
# ATHENA_NODE_BIN=bun
# Override profile / model without editing config.toml:
# ATHENA_PROFILE=default
# ATHENA_MODEL=qwen2.5-coder:7b
# Unlock the /godmode jailbreak toolkit (local red-teaming / research only):
# ATHENA_ALLOW_GODMODE=1
